{"id": "1435610635109929092", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "author_id": "179235663160279040", "author_name": "ellumi", "content": "i think the units are good, but the WoD and possee are mostly unfamiliar to me, im not sure caecus needs fortify running gluttony on him frontlining might be better, tawil and leigh are a bit iffy together because they both essentially deal 0 damage, keeping only oneof them (probably tawil) might be better.\n(tawil because aurita has good sustain on her own, but tawil could bring her back if she gets nuked in 1 turn).\nbut leigh deals massive damage on exalt alongside the arthi  limit + and heals, so do consider her as well.\nid heavily suggest u get aurita's WoD from the shop, its not premium so u can just buy it and it essentially makes her hp cost cards give 20 aliemus like a strike, hence two exalts a turn becomes very consistent in 6-7 arthi turns if she's surviving.", "timestamp": "2025-11-05T12:44:07.766000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["637072265741336578"], "reply_to": "1435454930864308265"}
